      "rationale": "Code verification performed using the method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver. Observed order of accuracy 1.97 (expected 2.0 for second-order scheme). Benchmark comparison against FDA critical path CFD round-robin (Hariharan et al. 2011) shows mean velocity error < 5%. Achieves Gradation 2.",
