      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed at the worst-case operating point (4 L/min, 3000 RPM, tip clearance 0.20 mm). Mesh sizes: 4.2M, 11.7M, 31.4M cells. Grid convergence index (GCI) on NIH: 3.1% (fine-to-medium) and 8.4% (medium-to-coarse). Observed order of accuracy 1.89. All production runs use the 11.7M cell mesh with GCI < 5% on the primary QoI. Achieves Gradation 3.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
