      "rationale": "Quantitative output comparison performed using E_val metric per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3. For NIH: E_val = 13.8% against 20% acceptance threshold. For velocity field: mean absolute relative error 4.2%. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed at all 18 validation conditions. Achieves Gradation 2.",
